<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Your Login Details - Easy Data Systems</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0; } .container { padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #0052cc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; } .logo {
      color: white; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; } .welcome-message {
      background-color: #f5f7fa; border-left: 4px solid #0052cc; padding: 15px; margin:
      20px 0; } .content { padding: 20px 0; } .details-card { background-color: #f5f7fa;
      border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; } .details-card h3 { margin-top:
      0; color: #0052cc; } .detail-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .detail-label { font-weight: bold; width: 100px; } .button { display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0052cc; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; } .password-box { background-color: #f0f4fa;
      border: 1px dashed #0052cc; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;
      text-align: center; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; } .security-note {
      background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 10px 15px;
      margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px; } .footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px; margin-top: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1 class='logo'>Easy Data Systems</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='welcome-message'>
        <h2>Your Login Details, {{firstName}}!</h2>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</p>

        <p>Welcome to
          <strong>Easy Data Systems</strong>. Your account has been set up successfully
          for
          <strong>{{company}}</strong>, and you can now access our platform.</p>

        <p>Please find your login credentials below:</p>

        <div class='details-card'>
          <h3>Your Login Information</h3>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Email:</span>
            <span>{{email}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Password:</span>
            <span>Your temporary password is:</span>
          </div>
          <div class='password-box'>
            {{password}}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='security-note'>
          <p><strong>Important Security Note:</strong>
            We recommend changing your password immediately after your first login. Your
            account security is important to us.</p>
        </div>

        <p>To log in to your account, click the button below:</p>

        <a href='#' class='button'>Log In Now</a>

        <p>If you experience any issues logging in or have questions about your account,
          please contact our support team at support@easydatasystems.com or call us at +44
          (0)123 456 7890.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Easy Data Systems. We're excited to work with you!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />
          The Easy Data Systems Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Easy Data Systems. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>123 Data Street, Tech City, TC1 2AB</p>
        <p>This email was sent to
          {{email}}. If you believe you've received this in error, please contact us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>